080\\u0099s like to coach against a former Zag on the international stage last summer at the 2023 FIBA World Cup in Manila, where he and Team USA ran into Kelly Olynyk and the Canadians in the bronze medal game.\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 445, \"end\": 451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"score\": 0.9999858505207762, \"rank\": 1.414946776081595e-05, \"text\": \"Manila\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\"}, {\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1905848855120363e-22, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 490, \"end\": 496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Olynyk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olynyk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Olynyk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Olynyk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt was strange last year when we played Kelly,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Few said during a media availability session on June 18. \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt was strange, you know, you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re rooting for him but then obviously you want to win the game really really bad.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Olynyk likely won\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t be the only pupil Few runs into this summer on the quest for the gold medal \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 in total, five former Zags spread across four different countries have been either officially invited to training camps or are set to compete in the Olympic Qualifying Tournament this week.\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 1064, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 585, \"end\": 590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"score\": 0.9999999814945115, \"rank\": 1.8505462379927573e-08, \"text\": \"Kelly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For reference, only one Gonzaga alum (Rui Hachimura) played in the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 5-on-5 basketball tournament in the 2020 Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1089, \"end\": 1096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gonzaga_Bulldogs_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.638834035210538e-31, \"text\": \"Gonzaga\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gonzaga_Bulldogs_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gonzaga_Bulldogs_men's_basketball\"}, {\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rui_Hachimura\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hachimura\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rui_Hachimura\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rui_Hachimura\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That said, four alumni could be making their Olympic debut this summer.\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s an updated look at which former Zags could be making the trip to Paris.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1341, \"end\": 1346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999972183105, \"rank\": 2.7817461426918385e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Players officially named to training camp rosters/competing to qualify for Olympic Games:  KELLY OLYNYK, CANADA  Olynyk got th