eries that kept the Pacers out of a 3-0 hole.\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2917, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2719, \"end\": 2744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_playoffs\", \"score\": 0.9999999999345164, \"rank\": 6.547016820826584e-11, \"text\": \"Eastern Conference Finals\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_playoffs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_playoffs\"}, {\"begin\": 2815, \"end\": 2830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_Knicks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0027432870394206e-75, \"text\": \"New York Knicks\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_Knicks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_Knicks\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 17 playoff games, Nembhard averaged 14.9 points, 5.5 assists and 3.3 rebounds while shooting 56.0% from the field and 48.3% from downtown.\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 3059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s unknown what role Nembhard will serve with the guard-heavy Canadians, though it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099d be presumed the 24-year-old will play impactful minutes for national team head coach Jordi Fernandez.\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RUI HACHIMURA, JAPAN  Hachimura headlined Team Japan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 16-man roster that was announced in late June, as the 6-foot-8 forward is likely to represent his home country in back-to-back Olympic Games.\\u00c2  While historic (Japan hasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t qualified in men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s basketball in back-to-back Games since 1972 and 1976), Japan doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t want to relive the experiences from the 2020 Games, in which it went 0-3 and finished 11th out of 12th in the final standings as the host country.\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3255, \"end\": 3268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rui_Hachimura\", \"score\": 